fileannotations-desc: Displays and edits annotations on file pages
fileannotations-go-to-filepage: It is recommended that you view and edit file annotations on [[:$1|the file page]], where they are available in a visual format.
apihelp-query+fileannotations-summary: Fetch wikitext and optionally HTML for annotations on a file on the wiki.
apihelp-query+fileannotations-param-pars: Whether to fetch the parsed annotations. Could take longer with many, large, or complex annotations.
